      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example features a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and a recent valve adjustment to ensure optimal shim clearances. The subframe has been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's known torsional stress points. Fitted with a square wheel setup for neutralized understeer and refreshed bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension, this M3 offers precise turn-in and exceptional lateral grip. A true driver-spec machine with a clean power band and sorted internals.",
